msgid ""
"**Tip products** can be created on the spot. To do so, enter a product's "
"name in the :ref:`Tip Product <configuration>` field and "
"click :guilabel:`Create` or press **enter**. The product is automatically "
"configured to be used as a tip at the payment screen."
msgstr ""

