"down menu, select :guilabel:`Print`, then select :guilabel:`PDF Quote`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/send_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:None
msgid ""
"Print pdf quote option on drop-down menu located on confirmed sales order in "
